snippet.title: Adventure Game (PS1/Net Yaroze) - Playthrough/Longplay
snippet.description:
Having already uploaded a Longplay of this a long time ago of this pain in the butt, the quality was horrible. But sicne I had obtained new software and was more patient with uploading, I might as well start re-doing them with better quality theys memorable treasures (to some) deserve.
